          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Linda Davidson kisses her husband John in front of his new (to him) 1962 Chevy Corvette dream care. She made a big gesture for her husband on his birthday, and he made a big leap of faith in trusting her while she pulled it off. This is one couple that will have you rethinking your relationship goals, because at the final chapter of your life, you deserve a spouse this awesome.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
